[b]ENFORCE WILDERNESS TYPE RULES.[/b]

What does this mean? Basically, this will enforce a set of rules applied to the wilderness switch, which will prevent people wielding P2P items outside the wilderness, and walking into a F2P wilderness. It will simply enforce rules and unwield their item, etc.

